title: Episode 1.3 | The Global Interior: Mineral Frontiers and American Power
itunes:author: Megan Black
description: Contributor(s): Megan Black | Megan Black explains how the Department of the Interior - a government organ best known for managing domestic natural resources and operating national parks - has constantly supported and projected American power
